To run the st-tests.py unit tests, you will need the following environment
variables set (shown here with an example path):

ESPA_UNIT_TEST_DATA_DIR=/LOSRLPGD02/data2/rockvam/level2_test_data
ST_DATA_DIR=/pcache/level1/dev/rockvam/level2/software/espa-surface-temperature/st/static_data
MERRA2_AUX_DIR=/pcache/level1/dev/rockvam/level2/auxiliary/LST/sample_orig_NARR_MERRA
ASTER_GED_SERVER=lsdslb:7480
ASTER_GED_PATH=/AG100.003/
MODTRAN_DATA_DIR=/pcache/level1/dev/rockvam/level2/auxiliary/MODTRAN_DATA
NUM_THREADS=4 (optional)

